Package managers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CourseSystemInterface
    Interface to be implemented for systems that handle course/index objects
    EntityManager
    Interface for controllers that handle entity objects directly
    StudentSystemInterface
    Interface to be implemented for systems that handle Student objects
    Systems
    Interface to be implemented for systems that handle user actions from UI and the entity controllers
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractSystem
    Abstracted system to be extended by concrete systems Meant to support Systems interface by allowing for non-final attributes
    CalendarMgr
    Controller class for DateTime related functionality.
    CourseMgr
    Controller class meant to handle course/index object related events
    LessonDetailMaker
    Controller used to create lesson details to be used by other controllers/entities
    LoginMgr
    Controller for handling login related methods
    StaffSystem
    Controller for the staff system.
    StudentManager
    Controller class for handling Student Entities
    StudentSystem
    Controller for the student system.
